text: Daniel Voiculescu (born 17 October 1956) is a Romanian rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Romania Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Dolj County
